@startuml
title From JDepend to Instability (data-derived)

actor User
participant "Makefile" as Make
participant "Docker: ce-ca-jdepend" as JD
database "results/*.jsonl" as R
participant "analysis/normalize.py" as Norm
database "results_normalized/*.jsonl" as RN
participant "analysis/build_dataset.py" as DS
database "analysis_out/dataset_*.csv" as OUT

User -> Make : make collect-coupling
Make -> JD : docker run (mount repo + results/)
JD -> R : write Ca/Ce per package (jsonl)
User -> Make : make normalize
Make -> Norm : run normalize
Norm -> RN : write normalized Ca/Ce
User -> Make : make dataset
Make -> DS : build_dataset
DS -> OUT : compute Instability = Ce/(Ca+Ce)\n+ store in dataset
@enduml